content: Holy sugary treats! Make the most delicious snacks this side of Gotham with help from this Batman cookie cutter. It features a sturdy plastic frame and comes with various pieces you can mix and match depending on how much detail you desire.

Build the suspense leading up to the greatest holiday of the year with this Halloween advent calendar. This spooktacular mansion stands at 37 inches tall, features a sturdy construction and amazing attention to detail given to every square inch.

Turn your horse into the belle of the ball this Halloween by dressing her up in this unicorn costume. All the other horses and barnyard critters will look on in sheer amazement as Buttercup gallops in wearing a majestic rhinestone studded horn with a matching tailpiece.

Show off your love for astronomy while you stay warm and cozy wearing this NASA logo sweatshirt. This crew style sweatshirt features a loose and comfy fit emblazoned with the iconic NASA logo across the front of it.

Transform your little angel into a beautiful Disney princess by dressing her up in this children’s Sleeping Beauty costume. This long sleeve dress comes with a convenient velcro closure in the back for easy access and a matching crown to complete the look.

Breathe a little life into any room by hanging up this amazing kinetic wall sculpture. This massive intricate work of art utilizes a single small gear motor to power a multitude of chains, levers, sprockets, and gears in continuous motion.

Balance your healthy eating habits by treating yourself to some soft and gooey homemade gourmet brownies. These delicious treats are prepared with all natural ingredients to ensure the best taste and can be customized with different flavors upon request.

Give your potent cocktails a lethal edge by serving them in these “name your poison” glasses. Each 11 ounce old-fashioned style glass in the set features a detailed etching depicting the name of a deadly poison like cyanide, arsenic, hemlock, and strychnine.

Give your home a little far east flair by hanging this impressive Asian dragon sculpture on your wall. This fifteen foot gold and black Asian styled dragon is masterfully sculpted and painted by hand to embody the symbol of power, strength, and good luck.

Add a little industrial personality to your home by lighting it up using this pulley wall light. This unique lighting fixture features a vintage Edison bulb that gives off an old school flair while the pulley system allows you to customize the hanging height of the light.

Turn your delicious cake into the focal point of your special day by accenting it with one of these custom geeky wedding cake toppers. These hand made works of art are customized with all types of characters from popular geek culture like Star Wars and Nintendo.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Galaxy Necklace
content: Carry the majesty of the cosmos on you with this glow in the dark galaxy necklace. Handmade upon request, the chain can be adjusted to your desired length while the pendant comes filled with a powder that glows in the dark after charging under UV light.

Make your posh party one to remember by delighting guests with these French macaron cookies. These vibrantly colored treats come in every hue under the sun and are handmade from all natural ingredients to ensure freshness and taste.

Create the illusion you’re evolving into a fearsome reptilian hybrid by placing this dragon spikes prosthetic onto your back. When laid over the spinal cord and adequately painted, this silicone prosthetic creates the effect that spikes are emerging from your back.

Give your home a unique retro feel any gearhead will love with this tractor coffee table. The table is crafted from  a real salvaged mid twentieth century Massey tractor front hood and is complemented with a sleek glass table top.

Give your formal wear a little second amendment flair by accenting it with these elegant bullet cufflinks. These custom cufflinks employ a real re-purposed bullet casing to make it appear as if you’ve got a bullet lodged through your shirt.

Look like a badass while you toke up your “tobacco” by roasting them inside this skull glass pipe. This five inch beauty is made from darkened glass crafted into a mean looking skull finished off with a 24 karat gold and pure silver plating.

Free up your hands while carrying Jr. around town by placing him inside this baby sling carrier. This handmade item features an elegant unisex pinstripe design and comes in a variety of various sizes so it can accommodate all types of parents and babies.

titleEN: World Of Warcraft Sylvanas Cosplay Set
content: Transform yourself into the baddest bitch in all of Azeroth by slipping into this incredibly detailed World Of Warcraft inspired Sylvanas cosplay armor set. This custom made set can be ordered in a variety of colors – making this a perfect outfit for BlizzCon.

Ensure your safety after society crumbles into anarchy by arming yourself with this post apocalyptic battle axe. This battle-ready instrument of death features a razor sharp circular saw blade designed to cut through zombie heads like a hot knife through butter.

Build up your fat layers for the harsh winter ahead by indulging in some of these mouth-watering s’mores cookie bars. A delicious blend of melty chocolate and marshmallows are glazed with a thin layer of condensed milk and placed atop a Graham cracker.

Chow down in true Jedi fashion by getting your mitts on one of these Star Wars themed quote forks. Each metallic fork comes engraved with a playful message reading “May The Fork Be With You” – a clever twist on the classic “May The Force Be With You” line.

Become the center of attraction at the next social gathering you attend by showing up in this insane Daft Punk fiber optic costume. The lights can be altered via wireless control and the suit is made from a breathable material that makes it ideal for performances.

Make already delectable pastries stand out even more by placing them inside these retro oven cupcake boxes. Each box is decorated in a fun style reminiscent of an old school ’50s era oven that protects your cupcake while you transport it.

Stay comfortable during marathon gaming sessions by resting your head on this Nintendo Game Boy pillow. Measuring 18 x 12 inches, it’s stuffed with fluffy fiberfill and features an incredibly soft fleece exterior accented with felt Game Boy decorations.

Accent your outfit with your favorite anime of all time by wearing this Dragon Ball Z ring. Available in both men’s and women’s styles, each ring comes available in different finishes and is crowned with a gorgeous golden four star dragon ball at the center.

Treat your taste buds to a zesty treat by preparing your next meal using a dash or two of this sriracha salt. Made using Kosher salt, it features hints of cayenne pepper and a subtle garlic extract that combine with the sriracha to create a truly amazing flavor.

titleEN: Skulls And Bones Embossing Rolling Pin
content: Give your baked goods a bit of pirate flair by preparing them using this skull and bones embossing rolling pin. The custom engraving on the rolling pin easily allows you to create dozens of ominous looking textured skulls and crossbones over the dough.

Turn heads wherever you go in this one of a kind ombre lace gown. This form fitting mermaid style gown comes with thick nude tulle straps that appear invisible against the skin and is accented by handmade roses for added contrast.

Show off your love for the simple country life by adorning your finger with this wooden landscape ring. Each handmade ring is crafted from birch plywood and sports a quaint little mountaintop village that’s carefully painted to give it a little extra charm.

Avoid blindly rummaging through your bag by storing your belongings in this clear makeup bag. The bag comes accented with a thick black leather border and features a thick clear vinyl body that lets you see everything stored inside.

Show off your love of technology while keeping your outfit fashionable by accenting it with this gold circuit board ring. This ring is geeky chic at its finest – the circuit board pattern is transferred to gold, engraved, polished, and topped off with a satin finish.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Zero Sculpture
content: Give your home a spooky Halloweentown vibe when the lights turn off by hanging this glow in the dark Zero sculpture. Your favorite phantom dog comes alive as he’s skillfully recreated in paper mache with a glow in the dark paint job.

Give your cosplay an incredibly realistic look using these Wolverine bone claws. These screen accurate bone claws are cast from urethane and resin and feature a sturdy yet comfortable aluminum grip that gives the effect the claws are exiting from your hands.

Give your cat a fun play area without cluttering up your home by mounting the modular cat house onto your wall. The set offers several different levels for your cat to lounge in and is coated with a special paint that doesn’t accumulate dust so it’s easy to keep clean.

Put on a captivating performance your audience won’t soon forget by dressing in these hand painted belly dancer silk butterfly wings. Each stunning pair of wings is handmade with a custom color scheme and designed to float through the air as you twirl about.

Make a loved one’s day of birth a little extra special by giving them this hilarious printer paper birthday card. The brutally honest quip on the cover comes printed in a vibrant color scheme while the content of the message is sure to put a smile on anyone’s face.

Keep your outfits stylish without losing any man points by accessorizing with this bold men’s wrench ring. The ring is cast in white bronze in the shape of a twisted spanner wrench and given a high polish silver coating that really makes it stand out.

Decorate your room like any self respecting Pokemon master would with this adorable light up Charmander. The lamp is expertly handcrafted in the likeness of the iconic fire type Pokemon and provides great ambient lighting for any room.

Turn mealtime into playtime when you sit down to dine on the swing set table. Crafted from steel and rich cedar wood, the table comes fitted with four swing styled chairs so everyone seated can swing back and forth as they chow down.

Arrange the perfect spot to relax in while gaming or just lounging about by using these vibrantly colored Tetris block cushions. Each pillow is handmade from polyester and is designed like the blocks from the iconic arcade game.

Get in touch with nature when you head out into the wild wearing this green leaf backpack. This earthy accessory gives you quick access to your mobile devices – its large enough to comfortably fit a tablet -and is made with a water resistant lining.

Keep your sweetie looking as radiant as ever by giving her this mini spa gift box. Each box contains small sample sized bottles of naturally made bath salts, body scrubs, and face creams designed to keep skin feeling great and looking young.

Keep your favorite literature close by at all times by accessorizing with this Harry Potter miniature book bracelet. This quaint little piece features tiny replicas of all seven books fully illustrated with an intricate level of detailing.

Set your high tech PC apart by giving it some old world charm with this vintage styled wireless keyboard. Hand crafted from copper, wood, and steel, it features plug and play functionality and features a slim profile that makes it easy to carry.

Add a touch of realism to your Halloween themed treats when you bake them using the anatomical human skull cookie cutter. The cutter measures almost four inches across and is ideal for cutting through dough, fondant, clay, cheese, and cookie dough.

Strike fear into the hearts of everyone when you complete your mighty warrior outfit with this LARP chainsaw sword. This lightweight plastazote weapon is made with remarkable craftsmanship and is easy to wield despite it measuring nearly 47 inches in length.

Power up your game room by decorating it using this Nintendo controller coffee table. This one of a kind piece of furniture comes styled like the iconic original NES controller and is heavily lacquered to provide a long lasting finish.

titleEN: I Am The One Who Knocks Doormat
content: Add an ironic touch to your trap house by accenting it with this lovely “I Am The One Who Knocks” doormat. The ideal gift for any criminal empire building entrepreneur, it’s made from eco-friendly materials and works best with indoor use.

Give any plain look a little exotic appeal by designing yourself a custom wearable accessory using the DIY henna tattoo kit. It’s made from all natural henna and comes with an easy to follow instructional booklet ideal for beginners.

Keep your city’s streets clean by transforming yourself into the ultimate law enforcer wearing this RoboCop costume. The body armor and helmet are molded to look like they are made from real steel but are actually crafted from lightweight plastic for easier movement.

If fun and adventure gets your juices flowing, this Star Wars BB-8 droid replica is the droid you’re looking for! Straight from the latest installment of the beloved Star Wars saga, this custom built droid will easily become the most popular addition in your astromech stable.

Cement your bond between you and your geeky compadre with this Star Wars inspired R2-D2 and C-3PO BFF necklaces. Available as a set or individually, each laser cut acrylic piece represents a half of this dynamic droid duo.

Give your contemporary phone a touch of old school flair using this original Game Boy iPhone case. The meticulously designed image on the back of the case will give your sleek phone the appearance it’s a classic Nintendo Game Boy.

Get the party going by giving your home bar a fun nighttime touch using these color changing bottle lamps. They allow you to easily change their color using a remote control and are available in a variety of different liquor bottles so you can mix and match.

Transform your budding terrarium into the Shire with help from this hobbit house terrarium set. The kit includes everything you’ll need to recreate Bag End, from a small version of the iconic domicile to yard accessories like a stone walkway and wooden fence.

Give any part of your contemporary home a rustic touch that’ll set the room apart using this mason jar vanity light. The industrial inspired metal pipe fittings combine wonderfully with the pint size mason jars to create a warm glow and welcoming atmosphere.

Give your backyard a touch of whimsy that’ll fuel your children’s imaginations using these fairy traveling caravans. Each caravan is handmade from natural materials like bark and moss to look like the adorable caravans of small mystical creatures.

Liven up any drab workplace by giving it a bit of character using one of these cardboard articulated robots. Handmade with an extraordinary attention to detail, each tiny robot features a unique design with fully articulated limbs.

Experience an old favorite in an entirely new way by sinking your cavity riddled teeth into one of these Oreo Rice Krispies treats. Your favorite dark chocolate cookie combines with gooey marshmallows to create a treat you’ll have a hard time putting down.

Transform your home into a scene straight out of your favorite sci-fi saga with this life size Star Wars AT-ST. Skillfully forged from recycled steel and auto parts, this all terrain scout transport stands at over eight and a half feet tall.

Stand out at the next formal party you attend when you show up wearing this steampunk top hat. It’s handmade with genuine leather and accented with opaque bronze rivets that contribute to the antiquated look and feel.

Keep your man mane looking majestic by using this beard soap and oil kit. The soap is made from a blend of all natural oils designed to provide a phenomenal lather while the oil is specially formulated from an assorted blend of essential oils and hops.

Channel your inner crazy cat lady next time you hit the water dressed in this one of a kind black cat swimsuit. This purrrrrfect one piece strapless suit employs a classic ’60s inspired design that is both frisky and flattering.

Give friends and family a unique gift that’ll add some character to their homes by purchasing this skeleton key collection set. This plentiful set comes with 68 antique styled skeleton keys that include a wide array of colors and sizes.

Marvel at one of Skynet’s most popular models up close and personal by adding this battle damaged terminator bust to your prop collection. It comes meticulously decorated with accents like hand punched real human hair for an amazing levels of realism.

Make your muggle courses more exciting by wrapping your books with these Harry Potter schoolbook covers. With your purchase you’ll be able to instantly download up to four distinct covers like “Advanced Potion Making” and “Quidditch Through The Ages”.

Keep your little one from freezing her heiny off during cold winter days by heading out in the kangaroo punch hoodie. The functional designs allows you to keep your baby comfortable and warm as you go about your hectic day.

Get on the fast track to morbid obesity by indulging yourself with some chocolate covered bacon strips. Each batch contains half a pound of juicy perfectly cooked bacon slathered with copious amounts of chocolate, caramel, nuts, and sprinkles.

Set your formal attire apart from the rest by giving it some unique gamer flair using these N64 GoldenEye cufflinks. These handmade cufflinks are skillfully crafted from polymer clay to look like tiny Nintendo 64 GoldenEye cartridges.

Let your love of nature shine through wherever you go by accenting your look with this moss terrarium necklace. This handmade item showcases natural moss in a transparent glass dome surrounded by an elegant eco-friendly tin border.

Create a unique antique feel in any room by lighting it up with this Edison bulb ceiling lamp. The inventive design of the lamp lets you place each independent socket in an arbitrary location so that you can control the lighting emphasis in the room.

Craft your friends some fun little gifts they’ll absolutely love without spending a bundle by following this DIY crochet Minion slippers pattern. The pattern can work for sizes ranging from 3 to 13 and is suitable for both men and women.

Take your disgusting levels of publicly displayed affection to new heights by ordering one of these customized couples stamps. It’s perfect for wedding stationeries, holiday cards, return address, and overall just making people despise your happiness.

Give yourself a terrifying reminder of the horrors that await when you forget to take your prescription by keeping it inside this birth control pill koozie. Its double stitched for added durability and provides the perfect way to conceal your promiscuity pills.

Step aside Teddy, there’s a new cuddle buddy in town and he’s looking to make a big splash. Modeled after the majestic humpback whale, this cuddly creature of the deep features a soft cotton faux fur coat and measures almost 30 inches long.

Brighten up your bathroom’s decor without spending a fortune by making your own custom soap bars. Following the recipe in the downloadable PDF, you’ll be able to craft uniquely shaped bars you can customize with any vibrant color and scent.

Keep your stress levels at an all time low by getting lost within the pages of the zen coloring book. Inspired by the meditative art of the mandala, each page displays a large and complex design that’ll keep you entertained while you slowly color in the pages.

Piece together a fierce pre-historic costume without breaking the bank by assembling this DIY paper T-Rex mask. Using this easy to follow PDF, anyone can craft themselves a cool and scary looking Tyrannosaurs Rex you can customize with any color you’d like.

Give your bedroom a bit of flair that’s reflective of your wild social life using these party life pillow cases. These 100% cotton pillows cases come printed with every twenty-something’s mantra to “sleep all day” and “dance all night”.

Pay homage to the your favorite gaming console while receiving serious style points wearing these Nintendo controller shoes. These slip-on canvas shoes are customized with printed on graphics to make them look just like the iconic NES controllers.

Track time like a true wizard using this Harry Potter wall clock. The edges of this geeky clock’s face are hand burned to create an aged look, while the numbers are replaced with Harry Pottered inspired references.

Keep guests at your Stars Wars themed party happy by serving up delicious snacks on this wood carved Millennium Falcon platter. Each platter is handmade using various exotic hardwoods – such as Hard Maple, and Black Walnut – and given a shiny gloss finish.

Keep yourself distracted at school or work by passing the time playing with this adorable mini felted sloth. This tiny guy features a cuddly sheep wool exterior and comes with wire paws so you can arrange your little friend in a variety of positions.

Keep guests warm on cold nights while giving your backyard some added accent lighting with this color changing firepit table. The LED center base cube glows in a myriad of vibrant hues while the fire pit within the granite countertop keeps you feeling toasty.

Turn bath time into playtime by bathing with these toy filled pokeball soaps. Handmade using all natural ingredients like coconut oil and oat protein, they make bath time fun by rewarding routine cleanliness with a Pokemon toy inside.

Creating the optimal sleeping environment using this rainbow trout lavender eye pillow. Shaped like a colorful trout, this organic  cotton pillow is filled with organic lavender and flax seed that create a heavenly aroma for you to enjoy while it blocks out light.

Spend more time with friends and less time going to get drinks by keeping them nearby using this drink cooler picnic table. The ingenious design features two built-in containers at the center that you can fill with ice and use as coolers for your beverages.

Give your Harry Potter cosplay an added touch of authenticity using this “I must not tell lies” temporary tattoo. The tattoo measures 2.75 inches across and goes on with a lot less pain than having the message carved onto your skin with the Black Quill.

Transform yourself into an eerie-looking seventeenth century physician by wearing this plague doctor mask. Made with an adjustable strap so you can customize the fit, this leather mask features darkened goggles and an ominous elongated beak.

Give your home bar or dining area a touch of style by illuminating it using this wine bottle light lamp. Clear wine bottles hang from a handmade cedar backboard with copper fixtures to give any room a rustic appeal while providing great complementary lighting.

Give your native american ensemble an authentic touch by topping it off with this real feather chief headdress. Handcrafted from the finest materials, it features genuine leather and real duck feathers for an amazing look.

Give your rainy day ensemble a bit of geeky flair by shielding yourself from the rain using this vibrant Pokemon umbrella. The umbrella is made from polyester, has a 41 inch span, and comes adorned with 19 cute Pokemon dancing along the edge.

Incite laughter wherever you go by trolling everyone around you while wearing this Deadpool costume. The suit can be hand tailored to your specific measurements and is made from an athletic grade stretch material that allows a full range of motion.

Experience your favorite deep space movie saga in a whole new way by passing the time playing with these Star Wars themed cards. Each of the poker sized playing cards are decorated with colorful watercolor styled images of the iconic intergalactic series.

Gear up for intergalactic warfare by slipping into one of these Halo Reach Spartan armor suits. This custom made suit is built from durable EVA foam and is weathered and rendered by hand to achieve a stunning lifelike appearance.

Get completely ship-faced by putting your naval skills to the test in a heated game of shot glass battleship. You and a friend will go head-to-head as you try to sink each other’s shot filled fleets and make each other consume as much alcohol as humanly possible.

Brighten up coffee breaks with a little wizard humor by sipping out of this Harry Potter references mug. This eleven ounce ceramic mug comes printed with a fun little quip that any fan of the books or films will find amusing.

Make your childhood dream of becoming a powerful fairy a reality by strapping on these Maleficent wings. They come with a corset brace for added comfort and support and are made using a mix of goose, turkey, and man made feathers for added realism.

Declare your love for your aptly adapted mate with help from the father of evolution by giving him/her this Charles Darwin love card. A portrait of the famed scientist graces the cover while the short quip makes a comical reference to his theory of natural selection.
